Package eu.ill.preql

Class FilterBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.ill.preql.FilterBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilterListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueryListener
    public class FilterBaseListener
extends Object
implements FilterListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of FilterListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
